50|$|In quantum gravity, {{the phase}} space is {{infinite}} dimensional {{as we are}} dealing with a field theory. An approximation which is sometimes taken is to only consider the largest wavelength modes of the order {{of the size of the}} universe when studying cosmological models. This is the minisuperspace approximation. The validity of this approximation holds as long as the <b>adiabatic</b> <b>approximation</b> holds.|$|E
